<meta name="date-created" content="2025 03 30"><meta name="date-edited" content="2026 07 05"><meta name="date" content="2025 03 30"><meta name="tags" content="kp2pml30,gamedev,design"><section><h1 id="sec-1">Best practices for game store pages</h1><ol type="1"><li>fancy thumbnail is a must</li><li>demo is appreciated, progress must be carried over</li><li>if game has a coop, there should be a discounted bundle for a few people</li><li>first trailer must show gameplay</li></ol></section>
